---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 301
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Necessity of Submission
  - 761
By: Epictetus
---
Know that the main foundation of piety is this, to have right opinions
and apprehensions of God, viz. That he is, and that he governs all
things.
